00:39:04,120 --> 00:39:05,240
Hello, Linlin?

643
00:39:05,520 --> 00:39:06,680
Hi, Ms. Jiang.

644
00:39:07,000 --> 00:39:09,960
There's something I haven't told you.

645
00:39:10,760 --> 00:39:13,360
Ling Yizhou and I are married.

646
00:39:13,880 --> 00:39:16,360
<i>Considering our identities,</i>

647
00:39:16,880 --> 00:39:18,640
<i>we've kept a secret from the public.</i>

