00:39:18,960 --> 00:39:20,600
But we now want to find a chance

649
00:39:20,840 --> 00:39:23,480
to tell the public and our fans

650
00:39:23,720 --> 00:39:26,080
the truth that we're married.

651
00:39:26,720 --> 00:39:27,640
<i>Don't worry though.</i>

652
00:39:27,720 --> 00:39:29,560
<i>This won't affect my work.</i>

653
00:39:30,520 --> 00:39:32,560
Why are you only telling me this now?

654
00:39:33,080 --> 00:39:35,080
We need to think about this first.

655
00:39:35,160 --> 00:39:37,120
<i>After all, you're an actress on the rise.</i>

656
00:39:37,200 --> 00:39:38,640
<i>You have to consider this carefully.</i>

657
00:39:39,280 --> 00:39:40,440
I know.

658
00:39:40,880 --> 00:39:42,440
But I still think

659
00:39:42,920 --> 00:39:44,920
it would be better
to be honest with the public.

660
00:39:45,000 --> 00:39:46,480
We'll need to see what the company thinks.

661
00:39:46,880 --> 00:39:49,000
By the way,
don't forget the fitting tomorrow

662
00:39:49,080 --> 00:39:51,160
for your red carpet outfit
for the Television Festival.

663
00:39:52,040 --> 00:39:54,080
Don't worry, I remember.

664
00:40:22,120 --> 00:40:24,600
Boss, it's late. You're not leaving yet?

665
00:40:25,840 --> 00:40:27,160
You can go home first.

666
00:40:27,240 --> 00:40:28,480
There's nothing more for you to do.

667
00:40:29,120 --> 00:40:30,240
Do you need help?

668
00:40:31,520 --> 00:40:33,160
Only I can do this.

669
00:40:34,960 --> 00:40:36,040
I'm going to go.

670
00:40:37,120 --> 00:40:38,360
I'm really going.

